@Agentic.Runtime.WebServer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5225

### Create a Response with Reasoning and Multi-modal items
POST {{Agentic.Runtime.WebServer_HostAddress}}/v1/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-5.1",
  "input": [
    {
      "type": "message",
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Perform a file search on the recent Q1 report."
    }
  ],
  "tools": [
    { "type": "file_search" },
    { "type": "web_search_preview" }
  ],
  "max_output_tokens": 1000
}

### Retrieve a Response by ID
GET {{Agentic.Runtime.WebServer_HostAddress}}/v1/responses/resp_abc123

### Compact a Response (Context Management)
POST {{Agentic.Runtime.WebServer_HostAddress}}/v1/responses/compact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "o3",
  "previous_response_id": "resp_abc123"
}